== Thanks for choosing Clever Monkeys Help Desk


Installing

1. rake db:create
2. rake db:migrate
3. rake db:seed

4 user will be created, the system administrator, support manager, the technical
support and customer.

Administrator

username: admin
password: admin

Customer

username: customer
password: customer

Support manager

username: support
password: support

Technical support

username: support_manager
password: support_manager

== Permissions

On page groups of users you can configure the permissions for each group.

== In the documents folder is the database model in MySql Workbench format

